snippet.textDisplay: Great video! I have been taking 5000 iu vit.d3 , for about a year and a half.  Didn't even catch a cold last winter. Not sure if that was why, but the vit d3 supplement , along with a multi vitamin seems to have made a high difference in the way that I feel. I am a 50+ yrs old  truck driver ,and worked through the pandemic, and have had direct risk exposure to sars covid 19 on a daily basis . So far so good. Love your videos, exllent content, and very easy to understand.  Thank you...
